# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __enter__, __exit__, __aenter__ across all 12 multiprocessing subjects
#
# Covers the full matrix: 12 classes x 3 methods = 36 rows.
# __enter__: true only for pool.Pool; all others false.
# __exit__:  true only for pool.Pool; all others false.
# __aenter__: all false — no async context manager support in multiprocessing.
# The concrete synchronization types (Lock, RLock, Semaphore, Event) are C
# extension objects; their context manager methods are not in their __dict__.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

